ANTICHRIST LINK VIRUS


                     Antichrist  is  a  link virus clone of the Travelling
                     Jack 3.   The virus add 2400  -  or 2404 bytes to the
                     lenght of an infected file.


                     The  texts  like "Antichrist"  aren`t  visible in the
                     virusfile.(Coded with a eor-loop). Antichrist creates
                     message_files on disks (and HD!)

                     Attention: This virus is only dangerous for kickstart
                     1.2 and 1.3 users. 


@Endnode


