         only  the  VIRUS counts. (SHI don't care, what "KIND" of disk you
         send  us).  After  the disk is analyzed the disk is formatted and
         your name,  will be 100 % arcivated in my trashcan. SHI....ALWAYS
         keep our promises!!, (no more questions then!)


         SEND A LETTER PLEASE: 
         An VERY EASY..way is to send the viruses to your regional center,
         who will then send them along to SHImain:


                                  @{"   SHI Addresses  " Link adMain}

